  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Videographer / Editor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview</strong><br />We are a personal training & buddy focused gym located at Sembawang/Canberra, aiming to help individuals kickstart their fitness journey in a fun and exciting way!</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong><br />BBF GYM is seeking a videographer intern to support the marketing team by creating engaging social media content through video shoots, editing, and filming client testimonials.</p><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Shoot and edit video content to produce engaging digital media for social platforms</li><li>Collaborate with the team to execute social media content pieces that align with marketing goals</li><li>Generate and develop creative video ideas based on current social media trends and audience interests</li><li>Film client testimonial videos to showcase client experiences</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Independent and efficient, with hands-on approach</li><li>Proactive and creative with a positive attitude</li><li>Good time management skills</li><li>Proficient in social media/digital marketing channels</li></ul><p><em><strong>Bonus Points</strong></em></p><ul><li>Experienced with motion graphics or graphic design</li><li>Interested in branding or marketing</li></ul><p><em>*Not required to be in the gym physically, mainly remote working: except for filming days or whenever required (minimally 4 times a month).*</em></p>",
